</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">The Transformers</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Skywarp insults Starscream saying &quot;he wastes more energy with his mouth&quot;, leading to the two quarreling for a bit before Megatron stops them as their elevator lands. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ITakeOffenseToThatLastOne" class='trope-example-link'>I Take Offense to That Last One!</a></p>
</div>
